text: Valorbiquet is a commune. It is found in the region Normandy in the Calvados department in the northwest of France. The municipality was created on 1 January 2016 and consists of the former communes of Saint-Cyr-du-Ronceray (the seat), La Chapelle-Yvon, Saint-Julien-de-Mailloc, Saint-Pierre-de-Mailloc and Tordouet.Arrêté préfectoral 9 December 2015 == References == Category:2016 establishments in France Category:Communes in Calvados
title: Valorbiquet
